104
00:07:09,679 --> 00:07:12,353
Maybe I'll buy a flat near you
and relive my student days.

105
00:07:12,515 --> 00:07:15,564
- Er... no, thanks, Dad. It's my turn.
- 'Yes, it is indeed.'

106
00:07:15,727 --> 00:07:17,695
Don't know where Jerry's going.
No, Jerry's getting lost.

107
00:07:17,854 --> 00:07:19,447
'So what are you gonna do
now you're retired?'

108
00:07:19,564 --> 00:07:21,111
