109
00:07:21,274 --> 00:07:24,244
Maybe I'll finally buy that boat
and sail around the world, you know.

110
00:07:24,402 --> 00:07:26,683
- You were gonna do that with Mum.
- 'That's true, I was.'

111
00:07:28,156 --> 00:07:29,373
Dad, I have to go.
I've got a big drive ahead of me.

112
00:07:29,532 --> 00:07:33,002
